{"type":"message","id":"a03c457a","parentId":"d8943054","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:55:13.590Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've completed the self-learning task. Let me summarize what I did.","thinkingSignature":"c1af2fc4c8ff90872394afba7f550a8ad63441aad5d94c8675138de056b64028"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n✅ 自主学习已完成\n\n**执行摘要**：\n- 空闲检测通过，无活跃用户对话\n- 搜索了3大领域最新动态（数字化转型政策、智能安防趋势、网络运维行业）\n- 整理5条关键信息，输出2213字学习笔记\n- 已保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**核心要点速览**：\n1. **数字化转型**：国家补贴最高5000万/项，工业数据筑基行动启动\n2. **智能安防**：AI边缘智能+预测预警（准确率98%）成主流，民用市场迎黄金期\n3. **IT运维**：AIOps全面落地（MTTR缩短40%+），外包从\"维修工\"升级为\"战略顾问\"\n4. **网络集成**：全栈监控+云原生成刚需，Kubernetes/Serverless普及率持续上升\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5413,"output":208,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49602,"cost":{"input":0.0016239,"output":0.0002496,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00319293}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775080507975}}
